  <Overview>
    <Title>Describe and Photograph Your Surroundings</Title>
    <Text>
      For one minute, please describe the room you are in right now, and the view out the window.
      Please use whatever language you are most comfortable with. Start by saying where you are (city, region, or country).
      Please speak and if possible, turn off things in the room at that make noise, like televisions, fans or air conditioners.

      Record your observations as an audio file at high quality and upload it using the field below.

      Please take a photo of the view out of your window, and upload that image in the second field below. Use whatever camera you have (a cell phone is fine).
    </Text>
